snippet.title: Bonesaw - Official Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1586860/Bonesaw/

Bonesaw is a turn-based psychological horror game with highly strategic gameplay and a stress-inducing saw mechanic. Plan your moves carefully to outsmart the devil or challenge the odds and gamble the fate of your fingers… and your soul!
